                                "stop": 8.827,
                                "byte_start": 86873,
                                "byte_stop": 122191,
                                "text": "The opinion of the court in number 94-500 Commissioner of Internal Revenue versus Schleier will be announced by Justice Stevens."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 8.827,
                        "stop": 102.346,
